#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/models/pos_config.py:0
msgid ""
"The Bancontact sticker payment method '%(method_name)s' is already assigned "
"to another POS configuration (%(config_names)s).\n"
"A sticker can only be linked to one POS configuration at a time."
msgstr ""
"De Bancontact-stickerbetalingsmethode '%(method_name)s' is al toegewezen aan "
"een andere Kassa-configuratie (%(config_names)s).\n"
"Een sticker kan slechts aan één Kassa-configuratie tegelijk worden gekoppeld."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/errors/http.py:0
msgid "The action could not be completed. Please try again or contact support."
msgstr ""
"De actie kon niet worden voltooid. Probeer het opnieuw of neem contact op "
"met de ondersteuning."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/static/src/app/pos_payment_method.js:0
msgid "The amount must be positive to use this payment method."
msgstr ""
"Het bedrag moet positief zijn om deze betaalmethode te kunnen gebruiken."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/static/src/app/payment_bancontact.js:0
msgid ""
"The cancellation could not be completed. Do you want to force the "
"cancellation?"
msgstr "De annulering kon niet worden voltooid. Wil je de annulering forceren?"

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/static/src/app/payment_bancontact.js:0
msgid ""
"The customer is currently completing the payment, so it cannot be cancelled "
"at this time.\n"
"If you need to cancel it, please ask the customer to do so on their device "
"or force the cancellation."
msgstr ""
"De klant is momenteel bezig met de betaling, dus die kan op dit moment niet "
"worden geannuleerd.\n"
"Als je de betaling moet annuleren, vraag de klant dan om dit op zijn "
"apparaat te doen of forceer de annulering."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/models/account_journal.py:0
msgid ""
"The journal '%(journal)s' is used by a Bancontact Pay payment method.\n"
"This payment method does not support the journal's currency.\n"
"Supported currencies: %(currencies)s."
msgstr ""
"Het dagboek '%(journal)s' wordt gebruikt door een Bancontact Pay-"
"betaalmethode.\n"
"Deze betaalmethode ondersteunt de valuta van het dagboek niet.\n"
"Ondersteunde valuta's: %(currencies)s."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/static/src/app/pos_payment_method.js:0
msgid "This sticker is already processing another payment."
msgstr "Deze sticker is al bezig met het verwerken van een andere betaling."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/models/pos_payment_method.py:0
msgid ""
"Unable to cancel payment. The payment may not be in a cancellable state."
msgstr ""
"Betaling kan niet worden geannuleerd. De betaling bevindt zich mogelijk niet "
"in een status die geschikt is voor annulering."

#. module: pos_bancontact_pay
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/pos_bancontact_pay/errors/http.py:0
msgid ""
"Unable to process the request. Please verify your configuration or try again "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Het verzoek kan niet worden verwerkt. Controleer je configuratie of probeer "
"het later opnieuw."
